data.description: Your search ends here, with this perfect home for your family! This beautiful, four bedroom, colonial home is nestled within the very desirable Woodbriar Subdivision. The first floor is expansive, with room for everyone to gather or have their own space. Rich hardwood floors guide you through the living room, dining room, kitchen and more. Newer Stainless Steel appliances throughout the kitchen, five burner gas range, an abundance of counter space, barstool seating, and a charming view of the backyard.The large family room, with gas fireplace, opens to the custom stamped concrete patio with integrated lighting. Additionally, your outdoor space is party-ready with a firepit, hot tub, trampoline, gas-ready for an outdoor kitchen, mature trees, no neighbors to the back and fully fenced for kids and pets. Upstairs hosts four bedrooms, two guest rooms with window seats, great closet space and new carpet (2020). The over-sized primary bedroom serves a retreat with gorgeous cathedral ceilings, a full primary bathroom, and walk-in closet. The basement is great for movie night, all set with a projector, screen, built-in surround sound and an area for a kitchenette. Woodbriar Village subdivision includes a community park with a playground and sport-court. Minutes from Downtown Oxford and Lake Orion, boating and beaches, commuting highways, along with many choices for shopping and restaurants, making this location a wonderful choice for you and your family!
